<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-02-27 00:50:27.300145</lastBuildDate><item><title>Please forward this to anyone yo know in Ukraine or bordering states.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/3vPlCWL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yBlibPQ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you can translate this for Ukrainians, please do! This very hour. If you know friends in Ukraine, or even nearby states like Poland or Moldova, please send this to them, asking them to pass it along to any Ukrainians they know. Do it now.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/so8S4Nu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6CNWZLE.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uWC38Ws.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GQgGco0.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MfNCUVE.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1nYqCm6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>EDIT: weaken roads from underneath in sewers, make ditches too big for tanks to span, put fake IEDs with wires in potholes to force an unarmored crew to come investigate. And thermite in a can with a fuse and with glue or magnets on the exterior. And: accept surrender wherever possible.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/3vPlCWL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jasonPositivityPilot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Because he’s very tough, and